1
00:01:02,359 --> 00:01:03,000
Stop!

2
00:01:10,079 --> 00:01:10,920
Shen Que,

3
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,280
this isn't the place for you.

4
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,560
Come with me.

5
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:24,000
Bai Weiran,

6
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,799
he's lying to you.

7
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,079
He can see clearly,

8
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,079
and he even scratched me.

9
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,079
When I first entered the room,

10
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,200
I saw you deliberately let him

11
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,439
scratch you.

12
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:39,640
Yes,

13
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:41,120
I did lie to you.

14
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:43,040
I don't want you to see anyone else,

15
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,359
or be kind to anyone else.

16
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,519
Don't you understand

17
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:49,000
why I did this?

18
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:51,760
Your Highness,

19
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:53,799
your wound

20
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:55,120
has healed.

21
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,040
In a few days,

22
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,719
you can leave the Demon Village

23
00:01:59,079 --> 00:02:00,239
and return to your mansion.

24
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,040
We saved your life this time.

25
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:04,120
Does this

26
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,879
wipe out my past

27
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:06,840
mistakes?

28
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:10,039
Can we

29
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,080
start afresh?

30
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:19,280
You think everything

31
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,759
we shared means nothing?

32
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:25,479
You started this.

33
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,759
Now you want to erase it?

34
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:29,000
No way.

35
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,280
Shen Que, are you insane?

36
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:39,280
Yes.

37
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:40,960
I am crazy.

38
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:43,400
I knew you approached me on purpose,

39
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,520
but I couldn't help being drawn to you.

40
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,280
I knew you were a demon,

41
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,199
yet I still

42
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,360
let go of everything

43
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,639
just to stay by your side.

44
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:51,879
I'm a demon.

45
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,319
You kill demons.

46
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,039
There can only be

47
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,199
hate between us.

48
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:00,719
Right.

49
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,800
I hate demons.

50
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,520
I kill demons.

51
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,800
But when I found out you were a demon,

52
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,240
I only had one thought in mind.

53
00:03:13,599 --> 00:03:15,439
Did you suffer a lot because of me?

54
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,759
Stop it.

55
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,199
Meng Li.

56
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,199
What do I have to do

57
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:29,159
for you to let go of our grudges?

58
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,800
Let go of our grudges?

59
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,960
Look carefully.

60
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,960
This is the Demon Village.

61
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:42,439
You're the Prince Xian with the order.

62
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:43,800
And I'm

63
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,400
the demon you're determined to kill.

64
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,599
We're born to be enemies.

65
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,560
It's either you or me.

66
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:52,919
There's no way

67
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,280
we can...

68
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,039
Enough.

69
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,080
I'm tired.

70
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,120
I need to rest.

71
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:00,879
A'Li.

72
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,120
Maybe

73
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,519
Shen Que's underlying dream has opened.

74
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,439
How could?

75
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:09,319
The underlying dream is moved

76
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:11,000
by the most sincere emotions of mortals.

77
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,720
He is now completely in love with you.

78
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,879
But I thought he was in love before.

79
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:17,839
A hundred years for mortals.

80
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,920
Human nature is full of anger, ignorance, greed, resentment, and hatred.

81
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,000
Love

82
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:24,000
is not just the moment of a racing heartbeat or intimate contact.

83
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:26,360
Love is against selfishness,

84
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,199
cowardice,

85
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,759
[greed,]

86
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,800
[and betrayal.]

87
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,279
[Love is feeling indebted]

88
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,680
[even when you know the worst of each other.]

89
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,360
[The moon shines alone,]

90
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,319
[the wind rises,]

91
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,279
[apricot flowers are scarce.]

92
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:19,480
[Reflecting on the past feels like a dream,]

93
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,160
[tears silently fall.]

94
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:30,160
[May joy and celebration last forever.]

95
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,120
It seems that everyone knows

96
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,920
making a wish at Leisure Chanting Spring

97
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,759
It seems

98
00:06:34,759 --> 00:06:36,480
everyone knows this.

99
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:37,800
How ridiculous!

100
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,560
Leisure Chanting Pool

101
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,600
is a sacred place for cultivation.

102
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:44,240
Yet the Ancestral Master wants to leave it for blessings.

103
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,759
What a waste!

104
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,879
I must ask the Master to take it back

105
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:50,319
for our healing and training.

106
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,079
Ah!

107
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,079
There's a demon!

108
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:32,879
After it!

109
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,519
Over there!

110
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:33,959
Hurry!

111
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:34,560
Yes!

112
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:00,920
Over there!

113
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,160
Hurry!

114
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,519
Help!

115
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:30,600
Don't let her get away!

116
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,000
Finally.

117
00:08:56,559 --> 00:08:57,799
Thank you for today.

118
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,200
My name is Meng Li.

119
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,399
You can call me Li.

120
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:01,759
What's your name?

121
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:06,919
You...

122
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,039
You're a demon hunter too?

123
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:11,399
Why are you still here?

124
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,320
How did I let her get away?

125
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,919
I hope you

126
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,679
can escape tomorrow.

127
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:57,600
After her!

128
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,279
Over there!

129
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:13,200
Hey!

130
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:13,879
Senior,

131
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,120
did you see that demon?

132
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:15,720
Ah,

133
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,639
We've followed her all the way here,

134
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,879
but now she's just vanished.

135
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:20,720
She ran that way!

136
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:21,840
Thanks, senior.

137
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,480
After her!

138
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:24,919
Quick!

139
00:10:34,399 --> 00:10:35,840
Why save me?

140
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,960
Little pixies like you

141
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:40,159
taste best when raised right.

142
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:40,679
You...

143
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:43,200
You eat pixies?

144
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,559
I didn't

145
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:45,559
I wouldn't.

146
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:48,039
But some pixies have such short memories.

147
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,440
They forget me so quickly.

148
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:51,960
This time,

149
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,720
I'll let it slide.

150
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,759
But if it happens again,

151
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,480
I'll really eat them.

152
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:02,279
[I wish I could see her tomorrow too.]

153
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:08,039
[Better yet, every day.]

154
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:11,159
[If I could see her in every life,]

155
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,799
[that would be even better.]

156
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,440
Daozhi.

157
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,360
Master,

158
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:18,480
didn't you always scorn making wishes?

159
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:19,879
Now,

160
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,519
why are you so devout?

161
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:22,960
To help others,

162
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,559
you must walk with them,

163
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,879
and imitate their actions.

164
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,879
That's what you said.

165
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:32,000
So, should we still tear down the pool?

166
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:32,840
No need.

167
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:34,679
With demons rampant,

168
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,399
it's good to leave the people

169
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,879
is a good thing.

170
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:46,720
I've heard that after coming of age,

171
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,200
demon clan will develop a demon hairpin.

172
00:11:48,919 --> 00:11:50,679
Why is the mark on your forehead

173
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:52,080
so dim?

174
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:57,559
Demon hairpin

175
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,320
needs Spirit-Guiding Sand to activate.

176
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:02,480
But I have no demon kin,

177
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:06,000
so mine has always been faint.

178
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,480
Does it have to be a demon kin to activate it?

179
00:12:09,519 --> 00:12:11,440
If you find your true love,

180
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:14,279
your husband can activate it too.

181
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,559
Who are you talking about?

182
00:12:16,559 --> 00:12:17,320
My husband.

183
00:12:32,399 --> 00:12:34,600
May A'Li find her Mr. Right soon.

184
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:37,240
May she be happy and content.

185
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,399
Can wishes made at the

186
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:43,480
Leisure Chanting Pool come true?

187
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:46,840
It is said that the other end of the pool

188
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,000
leads to the River of Forgotten Dust,

189
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,480
the Water of Destiny,

190
00:12:50,159 --> 00:12:51,759
which can grant wishes.

191
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,159
The Water of Destiny?

192
00:12:54,679 --> 00:12:55,799
Legend has it that only

193
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:57,559
[only the most powerful demons]

194
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:59,360
[can find the spring.]

195
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,799
[Even the hardest things]

196
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,639
[will melt away instantly]

197
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,879
[in its presence.]

198
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,600
Give me one.

199
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,360
I wish

200
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,559
Dao could always be by my side,

201
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,480
and he could be safe and happy.

202
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,240
I'm a demon.

203
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,639
You're a demon hunter.

204
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:39,000
I don't care if you're a demon.

205
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,279
[I only care]

206
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,639
[if you'll stay by my side forever.]

207
00:13:43,879 --> 00:13:44,679
[Year after year,]

208
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,320
[I'll light the hairpin for you,]

209
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:04,240
[and be your closest love.]

210
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,240
[Will you?]

211
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,360
[Li,]

212
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,679
[I, Shen Daozhi,]

213
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,639
[swear I'll never let you down.]

214
00:14:23,519 --> 00:14:24,600
[If I do,]

215
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,960
[may I perish.]

216
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,759
[This Five-Zhu coin]

217
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,279
has been with me since childhood.

218
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,039
I want to give it to you

219
00:14:58,919 --> 00:14:59,879
as a token of my love.

220
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,039
Li,

221
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,840
I'll go to my master tomorrow

222
00:15:12,159 --> 00:15:13,480
and ask him to bless our marriage.

223
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,240
Good.

224
00:15:21,679 --> 00:15:22,480
Master.

225
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,720
Master,

226
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,559
I have a request.

227
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,039
Daozhi,

228
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,480
you've come just in time.

229
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,840
We've finally uncovered

230
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,159
clues to the Demon King's Metamorphosis.

231
00:15:32,679 --> 00:15:34,320
She's taken the Demon Path.

232
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:36,240
If she completes the Demon Transformation,

233
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,039
chaos will ensue.

234
00:15:38,039 --> 00:15:40,080
The mortal realm will become a living hell.

235
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:43,080
Our duty is to find her

236
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,440
and end her,

237
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:47,519
to keep the realm in peace.

238
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,320
Daozhi,

239
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:52,720
I entrust this task to you.

240
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:55,000
Do not let me down.

241
00:15:55,279 --> 00:15:56,080
Yes, master.

242
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,759
For the sake of the people,

243
00:15:57,759 --> 00:15:58,919
I'll give it my all.

244
00:15:59,879 --> 00:16:00,679
Master,

245
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,440
where is the demon queen now?

246
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:05,159
She has taken the form of a dream-eating imp,

247
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:08,279
hiding in the Netherworld Cave near the pool.

248
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,399
Her name is

249
00:16:10,039 --> 00:16:10,799
Meng Li.
